## Analysis of the Main Target Image

The main image shows two separate structures:

- **Count & Layers**: Contains 7 blocks in 4 layers
- **Spatial Relationships**:

  - Second layer: One yellow rectangular block (#6) placed horizontally across both red arches
  - Third layer: Two green cubes (#3) placed on the yellow rectangular block
  - Fourth layer: One blue cube (#2) placed on one green cube
  - Top layer: One orange triangular roof piece (#16) placed on the blue cube

### Structure 2 (Right side):
- **Count & Layers**: Contains 3 blocks in 3 positions
  - Green rectangular block (#5) standing vertically
  - Yellow cylinder (#10) positioned at the base, adjacent to the green block
  - Orange horizontal cylinder (#9) placed on top of the green rectangular block
